Image Screens ID...31

The functions you use text as a parameter to are Vanilla JavaScript methods, and so expect a DOM node rather than a jQuery object. "This" by itself in this case is a DOM node. But, wrapping it in $() turns it into a jQuery object, which is then unusable by the functions you call later on.

Image Screens ID...33

The functions you use text as a parameter to are Vanilla JavaScript methods, and so expect a DOM node rather than a jQuery object. "This" by itself in this case is a DOM node. But, wrapping it in $() turns it into a jQuery object, which is then unusable by the functions you call later on.

            package Controllers;

import com.jfoenix.controls.JFXButton;
import com.jfoenix.controls.JFXDrawer;
import io.datafx.controller.FXMLController;
import io.datafx.controller.flow.Flow;
import io.datafx.controller.flow.FlowException;
import io.datafx.controller.flow.FlowHandler;
import io.datafx.controller.flow.action.ActionMethod;
import io.datafx.controller.flow.action.ActionTrigger;
import io.datafx.controller.flow.container.AnimatedFlowContainer;
import io.datafx.controller.flow.container.ContainerAnimations;
import io.datafx.controller.util.VetoException;
import javafx.event.ActionEvent;
import javafx.fxml.FXML;
import javafx.fxml.FXMLLoader;
import javafx.scene.Parent;
import javafx.scene.image.Image;
import javafx.scene.image.ImageView;
import javafx.scene.layout.AnchorPane;
import javafx.scene.layout.BorderPane;
import javafx.scene.layout.HBox;
import javafx.scene.layout.StackPane;
import javafx.scene.paint.Paint;
import javafx.stage.Stage;
import javafx.util.Duration;
import org.controlsfx.control.PopOver;

import javax.annotation.PostConstruct;
import java.io.IOException;


/**
 * Created by Daniel Kahiga on 12/20/2016.
 */
@FXMLController("/UI/MasterPage.fxml")
public class MasterPageController {
    @FXML
    @ActionTrigger("sell")
    JFXButton buttonSell;

    @FXML
    @ActionTrigger("products")
    JFXButton buttonProducts;
    @FXML
    @ActionTrigger("reports")
    JFXButton buttonReports;

    @FXML
    @ActionTrigger("closeWindow")
    private JFXButton buttonClose;

    @FXML
    @ActionTrigger("minimiseWindow")
    private JFXButton buttonMinimise;

    @FXML
    @ActionTrigger("maxAndRestore")
    private JFXButton buttonRestoreMaximise;

    @FXML
    @ActionTrigger("setFullScreen")
    private JFXButton buttonFullScreen;

    @FXML
    @ActionTrigger("help")
    private JFXButton buttonHelp;

    @FXML
    @ActionTrigger("notifications")
    private JFXButton buttonNotifications;

    @FXML
    @ActionTrigger("userProfile")
    private JFXButton buttonUserProfile;

    @FXML
    private HBox hboxWindowButtons;

    @FXML
    private StackPane mainPane;

   
    @FXML
    @ActionTrigger("showDrawer")
    private JFXButton buttonSettings;

    @FXML
    BorderPane MasterPageBorderPane;


    Main main;

    FlowHandler flowHandler;
    @PostConstruct
    public void init() throws FlowException {
        Flow flow = new Flow(PageLoaderController.class)
                .withGlobalLink("sell",SellController.class)
                .withGlobalLink("reports",DashBoardController.class)
                .withGlobalLink("products",ProductsController.class);
        flowHandler = flow.createHandler();
        //mainPane.getChildren().add(flowHandler.start(new AnimatedFlowContainer(Duration.millis(1000), ContainerAnimations.FADE)));
        MasterPageBorderPane.setCenter(flowHandler.start(new AnimatedFlowContainer(Duration.millis(1000), ContainerAnimations.FADE)));
    }

  @ActionMethod("sell")
   public void onSell() throws FlowException, VetoException {

        if (flowHandler.getCurrentViewControllerClass().equals(SellController.class)){
            buttonSell.setStyle("-fx-background-color: WHITE");
            buttonProducts.setDisable(false);
            buttonReports.setDisable(false);
        }else {
            buttonSell.setStyle("-fx-background-color: WHITE");
            buttonSell.setTextFill(Paint.valueOf("#000"));
            buttonProducts.setStyle("-fx-background-color: TRANSPARENT");
            buttonProducts.setTextFill(Paint.valueOf("#FFF"));
            buttonReports.setStyle("-fx-background-color: TRANSPARENT");
            buttonReports.setTextFill(Paint.valueOf("#FFF"));
            flowHandler.handle("sell");
        }
       /**Flow flow = new Flow(SellController.class);
       flowHandler = flow.createHandler();
       MasterPageBorderPane.setCenter(flowHandler.start(new AnimatedFlowContainer(Duration.millis(820),ContainerAnimations.ZOOM_IN)));
        */
   }
    @ActionMethod("reports")
    public void onReports() throws FlowException, VetoException {

        if (flowHandler.getCurrentViewControllerClass().equals(DashBoardController.class)){

            buttonProducts.setDisable(false);
            buttonSell.setDisable(false);
        }else {
            buttonReports.setStyle("-fx-background-color: WHITE");
            buttonReports.setTextFill(Paint.valueOf("#000"));
            buttonSell.setStyle("-fx-background-color: TRANSPARENT;");
            buttonSell.setTextFill(Paint.valueOf("#FFF"));
            buttonProducts.setStyle("-fx-background-color: TRANSPARENT");
            buttonProducts.setTextFill(Paint.valueOf("#FFF"));
            flowHandler.handle("reports");
        }
        /**Flow flow = new Flow(DashBoardController.class);
        flowHandler = flow.createHandler();
        //MasterPageBorderPane.setCenter(flowHandler.start(new AnimatedFlowContainer(Duration.millis(820),ContainerAnimations.ZOOM_IN)));*/
    }
    @ActionMethod("products")
    public void onProducts() throws FlowException, VetoException {
        if (flowHandler.getCurrentViewControllerClass().equals(ProductsController.class)){
            buttonReports.setDisable(false);
            buttonSell.setDisable(false);
        }else {
            buttonProducts.setStyle("-fx-background-color: WHITE");
            buttonProducts.setTextFill(Paint.valueOf("#000"));
            buttonSell.setStyle("-fx-background-color: TRANSPARENT");
            buttonSell.setTextFill(Paint.valueOf("#FFF"));
            buttonReports.setStyle("-fx-background-color: TRANSPARENT");
            buttonReports.setTextFill(Paint.valueOf("#FFF"));
            flowHandler.handle("products");
        }
       /** Flow flow = new Flow(ProductsController.class);
        FlowHandler flowHandler = flow.createHandler();
        //MasterPageBorderPane.setCenter(flowHandler.start(new AnimatedFlowContainer(Duration.millis(820),ContainerAnimations.ZOOM_IN)));*/
    }
    @ActionMethod("closeWindow")
    public void onCLoseWindow(){
        main.stage.close();
    }
    @ActionMethod("minimiseWindow")
    public void onMinimiseWindow() {
        buttonMinimise.setOnAction((ActionEvent event) -> {
            main.stage = (Stage) ((JFXButton) event.getSource()).getScene().getWindow();
            main.stage.setIconified(true);
        });
    }
    @ActionMethod("maxAndRestore")
    public void onmaxAndRestore(){
        if (main.stage.isMaximized()){
            main.stage.setMaximized(false);
            Image image = new Image("/Icons/Maximize Window-48 (1).png");
            ImageView imageView = new ImageView(image);
            imageView.setFitHeight(25.0);
            imageView.setFitWidth(25.0);
            buttonRestoreMaximise.setGraphic(imageView);
        }else {
            main.stage.setMaximized(true);
            Image image = new Image("/Icons/Restore Window-96 (1).png");
            ImageView imageView = new ImageView(image);
            imageView.setFitWidth(25.0);
            imageView.setFitHeight(25.0);
            buttonRestoreMaximise.setGraphic(imageView);
        }
    }
    @ActionMethod("setFullScreen")
    public void onFullScreen(){
        if (main.stage.isFullScreen()){
            main.stage.setFullScreen(false);
        }else {
            main.stage.setFullScreen(true);
        }
    }
    @ActionMethod("help")
    public void onHelp() throws IOException {
        FXMLLoader fxmlLoader = new FXMLLoader();

        Parent root = fxmlLoader.load(getClass().getResource("/UI/helpNotification.fxml").openStream());
        PopOver popOverHelp = new PopOver(root);
        popOverHelp.setAnimated(true);
        popOverHelp.setCornerRadius(10);
        popOverHelp.setArrowLocation(PopOver.ArrowLocation.TOP_CENTER);
        popOverHelp.show(buttonHelp);
    }
    @ActionMethod("notifications")
    public void onNotification() throws IOException {
        FXMLLoader fxmlLoader = new FXMLLoader();

        Parent root = fxmlLoader.load(getClass().getResource("/UI/Notifications.fxml").openStream());
        PopOver popOverNotification = new PopOver(root);
        popOverNotification.setAnimated(true);
        popOverNotification.setArrowLocation(PopOver.ArrowLocation.TOP_RIGHT);
        popOverNotification.show(buttonNotifications);
    }
    @ActionMethod("userProfile")
    public void onUserProfile() throws IOException {
        FXMLLoader fxmlLoader = new FXMLLoader();

        Parent root = fxmlLoader.load(getClass().getResource("/UI/Notifications.fxml").openStream());
        PopOver popOverNotification = new PopOver(root);
        popOverNotification.setAnimated(true);
        popOverNotification.setArrowLocation(PopOver.ArrowLocation.TOP_RIGHT);
        popOverNotification.show(buttonUserProfile);
    }
    @ActionMethod("showDrawer")
    public void onShowDrawer() throws IOException {
       
    }
}
